it's about power and money,
and that's freedom.

525
00:30:07,116 --> 00:30:09,352
God, Dad, I don't even know who you are.

526
00:30:11,662 --> 00:30:13,322
What you're becoming...

527
00:30:16,383 --> 00:30:18,945
whatever it is,
I don't want anything to do with it.

528
00:30:21,557 --> 00:30:23,363
I'd rather be piss poor with my dad

529
00:30:23,483 --> 00:30:26,035
than $13 million richer
with whoever you are.

530
00:30:51,465 --> 00:30:52,937
Holy mother of shit.

531
00:30:53,097 --> 00:30:54,405
It's Eamon Quinn.

532
00:30:55,723 --> 00:30:56,858
I thought he got life.

533
00:31:01,893 --> 00:31:04,949
How many people
