Frank Linehan, that's you?

535
00:31:08,696 --> 00:31:10,324
'Cause you all grown up.

536
00:31:12,760 --> 00:31:14,459
Ain't nobody gonna offer me a beer?

537
00:31:15,771 --> 00:31:17,698
I think you ought to leave.

538
00:31:20,889 --> 00:31:22,258
Little Ginny Dannegan.

539
00:31:23,356 --> 00:31:27,183
Last time I saw you,
you were about 12 years old.

540
00:31:28,216 --> 00:31:30,219
I always knew you'd be a beauty.

541
00:31:30,562 --> 00:31:32,894
