- Sure thing.

628
00:38:04,004 --> 00:38:05,832
Did you ever break parole?

629
00:38:07,225 --> 00:38:09,764
I ain't hanging out
with no more damaged men, okay?

630
00:38:09,884 --> 00:38:11,937
Now you just go, you big, old drunk.

631
00:38:12,057 --> 00:38:14,420
You take him out of here, Doug.
I'm calling the cops.

632
00:38:14,941 --> 00:38:17,037
Hugh, she's gonna call the cops.

633
00:38:17,157 --> 00:38:19,133
She loves this song.
This is her song.

634
00:38:19,538 --> 00:38:22,200
It's my house.
She won't even let me in!

635
00:38:23,446 --> 00:38:27,399
Oh, hell, Doug...
It just doesn't work without her.

636
