Yet bigger

663
00:39:49,925 --> 00:39:51,266
and more powerful,

664
00:39:51,556 --> 00:39:54,730
like $150 million...

665
00:39:54,850 --> 00:39:58,315
Bayou Hills, deal of the century,

666
00:39:58,475 --> 00:40:00,567
a lasting legacy to the genius

667
00:40:00,728 --> 00:40:03,027
that is Hugh Panetta.

668
00:40:03,340 --> 00:40:06,615
That's you,
the source of all your power.

669
00:40:06,775 --> 00:40:09,067
Gigi's Delilah to your Samson.

670
00:40:09,187 --> 00:40:11,601
She's kryptonite to your super...

671
00:40:12,049 --> 00:40:12,879
mojo.

672
00:40:13,678 --> 00:40:16,506
