675
00:40:24,710 --> 00:40:28,151
Well, I do know, Hugh. You got
to get some meaning in your life,

676
00:40:28,271 --> 00:40:30,678
the kind of meaning
that hard-focused, nonstop,

677
00:40:30,841 --> 00:40:32,892
100-hours-a-day-type work's gonna do.

